START    B     INPUT                    JINPUT ENTRY                    20700000
         B     FIND                     JFIND ENTRY                     21000000
         B     NOTELB                   JNOTELB ENTRY                   21300000
         B     POINTLB                  JPOINTLB ENTRY                  21600000
         B     ININIT                   INIT & TERM ENTRY               21900000
         SPACE 3                                                        22200000
