         USING *,R10                    ESTABLISH BASE ADDRESS          70200000
XTIN     LH    R3,DCBLRECL              LOGICAL RECORD LENGTH           70500000
         TM    DCBRECFM,BIT0+BIT1       UNDEFINED LRECL        @AX19477 70550000
